c Agent Findings ---\nBased on the metric data analysis for the abnormal event between 2025-06-11T01:10:22Z and 2025-06-11T01:29:22Z, I've identified several key issues. Let me provide my analysis:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"request\", \"response\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency degradation across all frontend pods with rrt and rrt_max metrics showing major increases\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt increased from 11826.95 to 34125.24 (190% increase), rrt_max from 223550 to 605899 (171% increase); frontend-1: rrt from 12309.33 to 36265.47 (195% increase); frontend-2: rrt from 12472.38 to 35112.02 (182% increase)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error ratio and client error ratio indicating service failures\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 7.95, client_error_ratio from 0.0 to 7.95, both showing significant error spikes\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated client_error_ratio and error_ratio suggesting service instability\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio and error_ratio both increased from 0.0 to 11.72 at p99 level\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory pressure affecting services running on this node\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased from 8.67GB to 7.88GB (9.6% reduction), potentially impacting services on this node\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Findings:**\n\n1. **Frontend Service Degradation**: The most significant issue is the latency spike across all frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2), with response times increasing by 180-195% during the fault period.\n\n2. **Service Failures**: \n   - checkoutservice-2 experienced high error rates (7.95%)\n   - cartservice-1 showed error spikes at p99 level (11.72%)\n\n3. **Node Resource Pressure**: Node aiops-k8s-04 showed memory availability reduction, which could be contributing to the service performance issues.\n\nThe root cause appears to be a cascading failure starting with service-level issues (particularly in checkoutservice and cartservice) that propagated to the frontend layer, causing significant latency degradation across the entire application stack.\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的调用链数据，我将分析异常事件的根因。让我详细分析这些trace数据：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->adservice\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend调用AdService出现大量'context deadline exceeded'错误（615次），正常响应时间约5.5秒，异常时高达499秒，延迟倍数90倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用PaymentService的Charge操作，正常响应时间13.8秒，异常时41.4秒，延迟倍数3倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用CartService的EmptyCart操作，正常响应时间20.1秒，异常时76.2秒，延迟倍数3.8倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用EmailService的SendOrderConfirmation操作，正常响应时间24.5秒，异常时68.5秒，延迟倍数2.8倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用ShippingService的ShipOrder操作，正常响应时间14.4秒，异常时64.8秒，延迟倍数4.5倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 根因分析总结\n\n**主要根因：AdService服务故障**\n\n1. **AdService完全不可用**：所有Frontend节点调用AdService都出现\"context deadline exceeded\"错误，表明AdService服务完全无响应\n2. **影响范围广泛